1:1 COMMENT "# io_protocol_rw.z -- project an open file through the `reader` and"
1:68 EOL "\n"
2:1 COMMENT "# `writer` protocols."
2:22 EOL "\n"
3:1 COMMENT "#"
3:2 EOL "\n"
4:1 COMMENT "# Exercises the full protocol-wrapper pipeline: file.write /"
4:61 EOL "\n"
5:1 COMMENT "# file.read are invoked via vtable dispatch rather than through the"
5:68 EOL "\n"
6:1 COMMENT "# file handle directly. Collection-type parameters (`bytes` /"
6:62 EOL "\n"
7:1 COMMENT "# `byteview`) travel by pointer through the vtable so mutations"
7:64 EOL "\n"
8:1 COMMENT "# (bytes.length growing after a read) are visible to the caller."
8:65 EOL "\n"
